:: chp1-why-can-cat-talk [dream]
The cat explains that this is a power granted to cats in dreams by the ruler of Dreamland. Her highness Julika. 

You keep hearing of Dreamland. So you ask the cat for to tell you more!

"It is a place that is not to different than here, except it is very old. Plus no cars. The rulers job is to ensure
dreams are not distrubed, that magic and happeniess is available for dreamers to grasp hold of." says the cat.

You ask how does one get there?

"Well, if you are not a cat then there is only way. You must have a ticket for the Dream Carrier. And before you ask, I
can not say more. There are many things you will have to discover for yourself." yawned the cat.

"But be warned, not all is happy these days around Dreamland. The evil Midnight Moon has returned. She will stop at
nothing to become the ruler." 

"My advice to you, is to write everything down in your journal. Please do give me some extra food to:)" smiled the cat.

You sense the dream is coming to an end. You have felt this before. The odd feeling that begins to come over you.

